1. How to delete a model group: DELETE /_plugins/_ml/model_groups/{id}
2. How to undeploy a model: POST /_plugins/_ml/models/{id}/_undeploy
3. How to delete a model: DELETE /_plugins/_ml/models/{id}
4. How to delete an ingest pipeline: DELETE /_ingest/pipeline/{id}
5. How to delete a search pipeline: DELETE /_search/pipeline/{id}
6. How to list/search models by model group name or list all models

